_data.text:
**ecosis Laboratories** is a ***Decentralized Autonomous Organization*** as the *Community Driven Core Team* for the **ecosis** platform.

We develop the ***Core System*** and its ***Infrastructure*** and we are the *Genesis Partner* of ***ecosis***.

### Approach

We focus on developing gateways with sophisticated technologies behind, so Users, Developers and Investors only need to get used to one.

Everything shall be reusable. Everything shall be automated.

We want an easy to use tool-set for the accessibility to build your own platform, which is scalable and customizable.

_data.text:
## Network

**eLABs** ***Tokenomics*** is running on the [Polygon Technology](https://polygon.technology/) and is deployed via [Aragon](https://aragon.org/).


## ELABS Token

*ELABS* Token is a **Governance Token**. You can use it for

- having Vote Weight
- writing Proposals
- getting Insights
- having the status of being an ***ecosis Laboratories Member***

This Token is especially stunning for

- Developers
- Investors
- Content Creators
- Exclusive Community

and ofcourse everyone who is interested into the project.

> Total Supply only 3,000,000!

### Rewards and Bounties by initial Distribution

Contributors get rewarded by ELABS Token out of *Reward Pool* until all Reward Tokens are distributed!

Contributions are:

- Development
- Content Creation
- Investments

and more the DAO finds interesting.

#### Token Allocation

- 40% Reward Pool
- 30% Initial Supply (Tokensale)
- 30% Genesis Contributors

The Vision is to build ready to use Web3 Template and Components with all kind of disciplines for

- Development
- Asset Management
- Public Relation

so everything you need for modern companies, but decentralized and autonomous.

## Autonomy
